{"tid":223543,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"[杜絕代購及Loreal group #1有懶人包] 化妝品護膚品討論區#40","createTime":"2017-04-30T11:53:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-30T12:28:17.000Z","uid":31133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"68cf836a9a1d3fc25e793bc77a5b89cf5e3c6c95","tid":223543,"uid":31133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T11:53:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">毋忘港恥<br />\n勿 提 L'Or&eacute;al Group </span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20160606/large/1465207186_6094.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20160606%2Flarge%2F1465207186_6094.jpg&h=8767be45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>LANCOME 事件重溫</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/19/024454_1668ad4871506d20ea533a2f2a7d88c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F19%2F024454_1668ad4871506d20ea533a2f2a7d88c8.jpg&h=3a21d078&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jeVp1h7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjeVp1h7.jpg&h=da6eb5e6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r5068KK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr5068KK.jpg&h=c30babfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/Lanc&ocirc;me取消何韻詩演唱會風波\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fevchk.wikia.com%2Fwiki%2FLanc%C3%B4me%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E4%BD%95%E9%9F%BB%E8%A9%A9%E6%BC%94%E5%94%B1%E6%9C%83%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusr5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=d293b0bb\" target=\"_blank\">http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/Lanc&ocirc;me取消何韻詩演唱會風波</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望連登妝post可以保持返高登幾十個post嘅良好風氣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">問問題前睇清楚#1及懶人包</span></strong> (e.g. 花水問題及其他熱門產品)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最好Google左先 對想問嘅野有基本了解<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 善用關鍵字搜尋e.g. Google打「xxx lihkg」或「xxx site:<a href=\"http://lihkg.com\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com</a>」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/24/233219_8dac5aec19ea44a84168ad7bf63ba618.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F24%2F233219_8dac5aec19ea44a84168ad7bf63ba618.jpg&h=4b78fabd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講清楚自己要求同基本資料<br />\n（例如：乾性皮膚想搵一隻滋潤光澤型嘅粉底霜，依家用緊XXX 覺得好乾...）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>如閱讀後有其他問題可以上POST一齊討論 唔好咁懶豬做伸手黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong></span> </span><br />\n<br />\n如果有絲打想幫人或者分享都歡迎PM GMAIL比波耶波囉咪 <br />\n<a href=\"http://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1YwXVV2da7D60nCgBB1R7O9IQNvAi7kUF4xEtm8w3LMs/pubhtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1YwXVV2da7D60nCgBB1R7O9IQNvAi7kUF4xEtm8w3LMs%2Fpubhtml&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusr5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=1d06aa35\" target=\"_blank\">http://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1YwXVV2da7D60nCgBB1R7O9IQNvAi7kUF4xEtm8w3LMs/pubhtml</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外大家可以留意下animal testing呢樣野, 有好多香港有既品牌都有做動物測試, 例如cdp, dior, shiseido, tom ford, fresh<br />\n想知個brand係咪cruelty-free有幾個方法:<br />\n1)<br />\n如果間公司係中國有實店, 咁佢一定有test on animals, <br />\n因為呢個係中國法律永規定<br />\n2)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.crueltyfreekitty.com/companies-that-test-on-animals/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.crueltyfreekitty.com%2Fcompanies-that-test-on-animals%2F&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusr5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=33ea9461\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.crueltyfreekitty.com/companies-that-test-on-animals/</a><br />\n3)<br />\n<a href=\"http://features.peta.org/cruelty-free-company-search/index.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffeatures.peta.org%2Fcruelty-free-company-search%2Findex.aspx&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusr5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=b222f4ad\" target=\"_blank\">http://features.peta.org/cruelty-free-company-search/index.aspx</a><br />\n4)<br />\nGoogle<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/564x/34/48/b6/3448b68470202f865371d2fe3537c94c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com%2F564x%2F34%2F48%2Fb6%2F3448b68470202f865371d2fe3537c94c.jpg&h=14033483&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1001左果個記得copy返呢度 D 野5分鐘內好開新post啦      <br />\n謝謝大家</blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"67e09de041f7562244b6da7224af0cf15fe60a61","tid":223543,"uid":7904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T12:28:17.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n開咁耐都無人既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}